Each service has a tag (`Context.GenericTag<T>("scope/Name")`) and a Layer that builds the implementation. `Layer.merge` combines layers with disjoint provides; `Layer.provide(inner, outer)` discharges inner's dependency on outer. The final `Effect.provide(program, AppLayer)` drains the `R` channel.

