Add a retry-capable fetch wrapper in fp-ts v2 TaskEither — start from this skeleton:
```ts
import * as TE from 'fp-ts/TaskEither';
export const fetchRaw = (url: string) => TE.tryCatch(() => fetch(url), () => new Error('fetch failed'));
